  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.poster.avif?t=1774095931\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.webm?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.mp4?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>For all the pixel art enthusiasts out there, brace yourselves for the quirkiest gaming experience! Meet Mike Melkout, the eccentric bellboy of a high-class hotel. While he may seem a bit off, even downright peculiar, he's on a singular mission – a dark plan, you could say. To clear out the entire place in just one wild weekend. Welcome to a humorous '80s-inspired point-and-click adventure, paying homage to the pop culture of that era. Get ready for laughs, nostalgia, and a dash of mayhem!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.poster.avif?t=1774095931\" width=620 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.webm?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.mp4?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br>• Beautiful pixel art graphics, full of 80's vibe.<br><br>• A unique story with lots of twists.<br><br>• Hilarious characters, depicting some famous 80’s icons.<br><br>• Funny situations and dialogues.<br><br>• Satisfying and balanced puzzles.<br><br>• Original soundtrack.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.poster.avif?t=1774095931\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.webm?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/4c839715c648e7643d31d8fdb69ed2da.mp4?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>For all the pixel art enthusiasts out there, brace yourselves for the quirkiest gaming experience! Meet Mike Melkout, the eccentric bellboy of a high-class hotel. While he may seem a bit off, even downright peculiar, he's on a singular mission – a dark plan, you could say. To clear out the entire place in just one wild weekend. Welcome to a humorous '80s-inspired point-and-click adventure, paying homage to the pop culture of that era. Get ready for laughs, nostalgia, and a dash of mayhem!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.poster.avif?t=1774095931\" width=620 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.webm?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1432200/extras/bb3845bb4acce669b468a750d1b40074.mp4?t=1774095931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br>• Beautiful pixel art graphics, full of 80's vibe.<br><br>• A unique story with lots of twists.<br><br>• Hilarious characters, depicting some famous 80’s icons.<br><br>• Funny situations and 